  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/c53a1d1f4eac241c2a9a507356d84586.avif?t=1765893039\" width=1560 height=640 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Final Knight is a strategy-driven action RPG inspired by the world of Dungeons & Dragons.</strong><br>In a classic fantasy setting, players form a party using a wide range of weapons, spells, artifacts, and items to face massive bosses that threaten the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Combat</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outside of your directly controlled character, allies act automatically.<br>Take advantage of the <strong>Tactical Command (time-stop) system</strong>, inspired by CRPGs, to pause the battle and issue orders with precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamlessly switch between characters in real time—taunt enemies as the Warrior, unleash Meteor as the Wizard, perform a Backstep as the Rogue, or cast healing spells as the Cleric—chaining them together into powerful combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/d0b99d521e1dfed3aef9bdac6d715a63.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/d0b99d521e1dfed3aef9bdac6d715a63.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/d0b99d521e1dfed3aef9bdac6d715a63.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Party Building</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose <strong>4 characters out of 9 distinct classes</strong> to form your party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each class fulfills a fundamental role—Tank, Damage Dealer, or Support—and can further specialize through leveling, advanced job changes, and stat growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>unique feats from equipment</strong> and the <strong>Formation system</strong> that alters party positioning, you can craft and execute your own strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/57e562b6ec85db74e2aa55f1e307426d.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/57e562b6ec85db74e2aa55f1e307426d.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/57e562b6ec85db74e2aa55f1e307426d.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Growth Paths</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every party member can progress in multiple ways:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced job changes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlocking unique feats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mastery upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting and fusing equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear enhancement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discovering bonds between characters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your team evolves endlessly along the paths you choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/53d2c29df2e086797752ad4ff6f0cf81.avif?t=1765893039\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Endless Gameplay Loop</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on raid-style battles against powerful bosses.<br>Break their weak points, harvest materials, and forge new equipment.<br>When enemies are staggered, unleash devastating combos by combining strategy with precise controls to bring them down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Play <strong>offline 2-player co-op</strong>, experiment with skill synergies, and discover new ways to combine abilities with a friend.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/c53a1d1f4eac241c2a9a507356d84586.avif?t=1765893039\" width=1560 height=640 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Final Knight is a strategy-driven action RPG inspired by the world of Dungeons & Dragons.</strong><br>In a classic fantasy setting, players form a party using a wide range of weapons, spells, artifacts, and items to face massive bosses that threaten the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Combat</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outside of your directly controlled character, allies act automatically.<br>Take advantage of the <strong>Tactical Command (time-stop) system</strong>, inspired by CRPGs, to pause the battle and issue orders with precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamlessly switch between characters in real time—taunt enemies as the Warrior, unleash Meteor as the Wizard, perform a Backstep as the Rogue, or cast healing spells as the Cleric—chaining them together into powerful combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"htt