ragraph\" >Every party member can progress in multiple ways:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced job changes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlocking unique feats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mastery upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting and fusing equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear enhancement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discovering bonds between characters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your team evolves endlessly along the paths you choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/53d2c29df2e086797752ad4ff6f0cf81.avif?t=1765893039\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Endless Gameplay Loop</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on raid-style battles against powerful bosses.<br>Break their weak points, harvest materials, and forge new equipment.<br>When enemies are staggered, unleash devastating combos by combining strategy with precise controls to bring them down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Local Multiplayer</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Play <strong>offline 2-player co-op</strong>, experiment with skill synergies, and discover new ways to combine abilities with a friend.</p>",
